1
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,580
♪Flowers falling by the river again♪

2
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:38,840
♪Turning the clear waves red♪

3
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,600
♪Sparrows singing in celebration♪

4
00:00:46,290 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Calm years pass by the silent bustling city♪

5
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:52,070
♪Sitting at home♪

6
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:58,260
♪No one knows love's outline like I do♪

7
00:00:58,550 --> 00:01:04,640
♪If one day the river breeze blows again♪

8
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,980
♪I won't be a mere reflection in the mirror♪

9
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:17,540
♪Dreams can shatter; Memories remain♪

10
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:21,230
♪Rich fragrance aids; Light ink writes♪

11
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:28,090
♪In the deep red windows lies mundane dust♪

12
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:40,980
=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 4=

14
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,300
Anyone here?

15
00:01:54,970 --> 00:01:56,810
Are you Mr. Hate Brush?

16
00:01:56,810 --> 00:01:58,020
Mr. Chen Shi?

17
00:02:05,380 --> 00:02:09,460
(Throw Away the Ink)

18
00:02:11,050 --> 00:02:12,380
Mr. Hate Brush.

19
00:02:13,650 --> 00:02:15,910
Your title suits you well.

20
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,130
The brush is so hateful.

21
00:02:18,330 --> 00:02:19,870
I wish I could break it

22
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:22,190
and never paint again.

23
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,240
Fangxie.

24
00:02:44,210 --> 00:02:45,880
I have some thoughts

25
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,160
on this painting.

26
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,000
I wonder if you

27
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,210
would be willing to hear them.

28
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:50,260
Please go ahead.

29
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,070
Later, I'll have to chop wood and cook.

30
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,150
In the eyes of this dragonfly,

31
00:02:55,770 --> 00:02:57,220
I see a graceful figure.

32
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,870
A woman holding an umbrella.

33
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:02,900
You have sharp eyes.

34
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:06,170
My Lord,

35
00:03:06,490 --> 00:03:07,940
the bandits aren't here.

36
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:09,260
She came for the painting.

37
00:03:09,770 --> 00:03:11,430
Why is she looking at the painting?

38
00:03:11,970 --> 00:03:13,820
Your brushwork is superb,

39
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:15,150
but in my opinion,

40
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,430
the most skillful part of the painting

41
00:03:17,770 --> 00:03:18,870
is not the dragonfly's eyes.

42
00:03:19,650 --> 00:03:21,870
(Mr. Hate Brush)
It's the seal.

43
00:03:23,090 --> 00:03:23,970
I didn't expect you

44
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:25,870
to be an expert in seal carving too.

45
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,590
My husband deals in porcelain.

46
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:30,940
You are skilled at carving porcelain seals.

47
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:32,650
If you could apply this skill

48
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:33,980
to our porcelain,

49
00:03:34,370 --> 00:03:36,150
you'd make your name in Zhenzhou.

50
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,150
To be honest,

51
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:40,910
our porcelain shop isn't doing well.

52
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,350
Many stores have already closed.

53
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:45,090
We came to Lingquan Town

54
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:46,540
to start anew.

55
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,910
My husband is a kind man.

56
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:52,220
He wanted to give me peace of mind

57
00:03:52,490 --> 00:03:53,470
and clear my name,

58
00:03:53,930 --> 00:03:54,910
so he spent

59
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,780
all our remaining money

60
00:03:57,210 --> 00:03:58,150
to host a grand banquet.

61
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,260
He hid this from me

62
00:04:03,090 --> 00:04:04,820
yet gave me the best house

63
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,720
and the most expensive scented powder.

64
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,560
But he has to face the end

65
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,470
of our business alone.

66
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,260
Now, he's even playing Go.

67
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:16,990
If we can't succeed

68
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,670
in Lingquan Town,

69
00:04:20,770 --> 00:04:21,870
I'm afraid my husband

70
00:04:22,890 --> 00:04:24,460
will be tormented inside.

71
00:04:25,970 --> 00:04:27,190
As his wife,

72
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:28,900
I've drained his fortune.

73
00:04:29,650 --> 00:04:31,380
I have nothing to give him to start anew.

74
00:04:32,970 --> 00:04:34,230
All I have is my sincerity,

75
00:04:34,690 --> 00:04:35,820
hoping to move you

76
00:04:36,090 --> 00:04:37,260
to use your godly skills

77
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:39,430
to help us rebuild our business.

78
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,230
There are many who can carve seals.

79
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:46,230
Why did you choose me?

80
00:04:46,650 --> 00:04:48,790
Because of the dragonfly in this painting?

81
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:50,870
I guess

82
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,820
the graceful woman

83
00:04:53,870 --> 00:04:55,260
is your wife, right?

84
00:04:58,310 --> 00:04:59,580
The dragonfly is near the water,

85
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:02,110
but its eyes don't see the lotus.

86
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:05,260
Because when you're in love with someone,

87
00:05:06,330 --> 00:05:08,900
they're the only ones you can see.

88
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,140
Cui Jiu is truly blessed.

89
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:19,160
If you agree,

90
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,260
I will pay you generously.

91
00:05:21,010 --> 00:05:22,140
I don't agree.

92
00:05:22,890 --> 00:05:23,730
Sir.

93
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,760
Sir.

94
00:05:35,650 --> 00:05:36,490
Sir.

95
00:05:38,770 --> 00:05:39,610
Originally,

96
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:42,500
I could have achieved great things.

97
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,460
But I loved painting.

98
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:49,260
My wife was understanding.

99
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:52,400
At that time, she believed in me,

100
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,670
just like you do now.

101
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,340
As a result,

102
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,670
I painted for ten years

103
00:05:59,010 --> 00:06:00,900
but never succeeded.

104
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,670
We lived in a shabby house,

105
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:04,340
struggling to make ends meet.

106
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,550
Even when my wife was gravely ill,

107
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,870
I couldn't afford medicine.

108
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:13,430
My wife, like you,

109
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,500
gave everything

110
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,570
for a worthless man.

111
00:06:17,570 --> 00:06:18,430
In the end,

112
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,360
she was

113
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,140
buried here alone,

114
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:24,310
left to the wind and rain.

115
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,310
So forgive me.

116
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,700
I can't agree.

117
00:06:29,010 --> 00:06:29,850
Sir.

118
00:06:30,090 --> 00:06:31,670
My husband is not a worthless man.

119
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:34,750
If he wants to rebuild your business,

120
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:36,790
why didn't he come with you?

121
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,500
Sir, you misunderstand.

122
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,560
My husband, he...

123
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,750
- He just...
- Just arrived late.

124
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,230
I'm Cui Jiu.

125
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:52,550
I hope you will use your skills

126
00:06:52,770 --> 00:06:54,310
to fulfill my wife's wish.

127
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,000
Ms. Liu, wait.

128
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:08,940
- What?
- What do you mean?

129
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,480
Ms. Liu and I

130
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,190
were appreciating the painting,

131
00:07:12,690 --> 00:07:13,900
and you suddenly appeared

132
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,080
and ruined the mood.

133
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,560
Jealous?

134
00:07:20,010 --> 00:07:21,450
I arranged everything.

135
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:22,570
I let her find Lu Wen.

136
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:23,900
You took her to see the painting.

137
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,990
If I hadn't appeared,

138
00:07:26,450 --> 00:07:27,550
given her temperament,

139
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,260
she would come

140
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:30,500
every day.

141
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,670
How can I catch Lu Wen?

142
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:34,460
That's your problem.

143
00:07:35,710 --> 00:07:36,880
It has nothing to do with me.

144
00:07:40,010 --> 00:07:40,990
You did it on purpose.

145
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:42,750
I'm a physician.

146
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,700
Physicians are compassionate.

147
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:46,400
I can't stand seeing my patients

148
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,310
being used

149
00:07:47,530 --> 00:07:49,020
and ending up badly.

150
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,640
Don't do it again.

151
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,820
Why should I listen to you?

152
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,640
I make my own rules.

153
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,240
I'll do it every day

154
00:08:04,650 --> 00:08:05,490
to annoy you.

155
00:08:06,970 --> 00:08:09,110
Don't meet Zhao anymore.

156
00:08:10,130 --> 00:08:11,260
We are husband and wife.

157
00:08:11,650 --> 00:08:13,070
He should stay within his bounds.

158
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,840
He even made excuses

159
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,230
to take you to see that painter.

160
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,190
He almost...

161
00:08:19,570 --> 00:08:20,870
He almost broke my rules.

162
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,240
You too.

163
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,670
It was my oversight.

164
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:26,450
I was only thinking about the shop,

165
00:08:26,450 --> 00:08:27,380
ignoring your feelings.

166
00:08:28,570 --> 00:08:30,010
Fortunately, you came.

167
00:08:30,010 --> 00:08:31,870
Mr. Hate Brush finally agreed,

168
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,700
charging us the price of one painting.

169
00:08:36,930 --> 00:08:37,770
Jealous?

170
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,720
No.

171
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,480
Not at all.

172
00:08:48,210 --> 00:08:49,070
Jiu,

173
00:08:49,330 --> 00:08:51,190
is something troubling you?

174
00:08:54,090 --> 00:08:55,030
Why do you ask?

175
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,840
I just feel like your mood

176
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,940
has been up and down lately.

177
00:08:59,170 --> 00:09:00,930
Sometimes you smile; sometimes you frown.

178
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:02,220
You keep holding back

179
00:09:03,090 --> 00:09:04,640
things you wanna say.

180
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,810
It's like you've been wronged

181
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:07,220
but have no one to talk to.

182
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:11,100
You're overthinking.

183
00:09:11,930 --> 00:09:12,860
I know

184
00:09:13,170 --> 00:09:14,790
you're keeping something from me.

185
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,220
It's fine if you

186
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,790
don't want to tell me.

187
00:09:20,330 --> 00:09:21,670
I just hope that one day,

188
00:09:22,210 --> 00:09:23,790
we'll be open with each other.

189
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,980
Jiu, you can trust me.

190
00:09:26,210 --> 00:09:27,910
No matter what challenges we face,

191
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,600
I'll stay by your side

192
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,670
wholeheartedly.

193
00:09:31,290 --> 00:09:32,790
As long as we stand together as one,

194
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:34,430
we'll get through it.

195
00:09:43,930 --> 00:09:44,770
Thank you.

196
00:09:48,050 --> 00:09:48,890
And

197
00:09:51,170 --> 00:09:52,480
remember to take the medicine

198
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,860
from Physician Zhao on time.

199
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:56,150
It'll help you recover faster.

200
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,510
Don't mention that Physician Zhao again.

201
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,030
I'm perfectly fine.

202
00:10:08,620 --> 00:10:09,460
(Lingquan Town)

203
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,450
Hurry, hurry.

204
00:10:10,450 --> 00:10:11,390
Get ready to set sail.

205
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:12,810
Coming.

206
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,690
Come on, watch your step.

207
00:10:17,690 --> 00:10:18,620
- Thank you.
- Come on.

208
00:10:18,970 --> 00:10:19,810
Take it slow.

209
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,340
What are you waiting for? Get on the boat.

210
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:26,170
Wait a little longer.

211
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,680
General Huang.

212
00:10:34,290 --> 00:10:35,130
How is Liu?

213
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,450
She's been staying in the house.

214
00:10:37,450 --> 00:10:38,670
No signs of leaving.

215
00:10:39,690 --> 00:10:40,530
What about you?

216
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,600
They're all there.

217
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,340
Waiting for her.

218
00:10:51,450 --> 00:10:52,290
My lord.

219
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,680
Keep watching.

220
00:10:53,970 --> 00:10:54,820
- Yes.
- Yes.

221
00:10:58,570 --> 00:10:59,940
If Liu Miantang dares to come,

222
00:11:00,290 --> 00:11:01,150
she won't leave.

223
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,640
By then,

224
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:03,980
we can either feed her to the fish

225
00:11:04,210 --> 00:11:05,310
or bring her to the master.

226
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,790
The decision will be yours.

227
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,700
She still hasn't shown up.

228
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:13,220
Could it be that she's completely forgotten

229
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,940
the code from Mount Yang?

230
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,580
Young Master...

231
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:21,890
Miss.

232
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,080
Stop waiting.

233
00:11:40,450 --> 00:11:41,290
Let's go.

234
00:11:42,930 --> 00:11:43,860
Why are they leaving?

235
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:46,670
Did they spot us?

236
00:11:49,050 --> 00:11:50,100
Hold on.

237
00:11:50,970 --> 00:11:51,910
Wait, wait!

238
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:57,390
Hurry up! Hurry up!

239
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:58,720
Slow down.

240
00:11:59,970 --> 00:12:01,030
You're wise, My Lord.

241
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,980
Look, My Lord.

242
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:22,700
The Chief Commander of Qingzhou.

243
00:12:23,970 --> 00:12:24,940
Shi Yikuan.

244
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:26,870
(Cui Mansion)
Chief Commander?

245
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:28,150
Who is this?

246
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,510
He's Lord Huaiyang in Qingzhou.

247
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,480
Qingzhou is

248
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,880
next to our Zhenzhou.

249
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:35,270
There were bandit troubles before.

250
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,090
I've heard the Chief Commander
and Lord Huaiyang have been

251
00:12:38,090 --> 00:12:39,390
competing to catch the bandits.

252
00:12:39,690 --> 00:12:40,880
If I were them,

253
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,220
why bother with the bandits?

254
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,690
I'd just burn Mount Yang to the ground.

255
00:12:44,690 --> 00:12:46,410
- Impressive.
- Look at you!

256
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:47,260
Aren't I clever?

257
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:49,050
Why are you still sitting here?

258
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,570
The Cui porcelain shop is opening.

259
00:12:50,570 --> 00:12:51,760
Why not join the fun?

260
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,640
It's opening?

261
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,720
Let's go check it out.

262
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,560
- Let's go.
- Go.

263
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:56,720
Where did you hear that?

264
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,910
Everyone's talking about it.

265
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,920
What a lively scene!

266
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:10,060
(Yushao Porcelain Shop)

267
00:13:14,170 --> 00:13:15,700
Take a look!

268
00:13:17,050 --> 00:13:18,720
Freshly made! Come and see!

269
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,100
Look at all these people.

270
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,680
Let's go.

271
00:13:32,690 --> 00:13:34,700
Mrs. Cui, may your business prosper!

272
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:36,690
- Take your time.
- Sure.

273
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,290
Whether it prospers

274
00:13:38,290 --> 00:13:39,570
depends on all of you, ladies,

275
00:13:39,570 --> 00:13:40,580
to help me out.

276
00:13:40,930 --> 00:13:42,900
Of course.

277
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,240
(Five taels)

278
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,190
Of course.

279
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:47,390
So expensive!

280
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,600
Jade pillow with curtain.

281
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,790
The coolness seeps through.

282
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:52,240
This porcelain pillow is as smooth as jade,

283
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:54,070
with a color slightly lighter than sky blue.

284
00:13:54,290 --> 00:13:55,310
A top-quality item.

285
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:57,030
Mrs. Yin, you have an eye for quality.

286
00:13:57,690 --> 00:13:58,530
Of course.

287
00:13:58,640 --> 00:13:59,640
In my porcelain workshop,

288
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,510
each item goes through 72 processes,

289
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,410
all personally overseen by me.

290
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:04,790
Rest assured and take your pick.

291
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,570
Who would've thought Mrs. Cui,

292
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:07,910
