293
00:14:08,170 --> 00:14:09,340
has already become an expert?

294
00:14:12,690 --> 00:14:13,720
Look. So beautiful.

295
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,220
On such a joyous day,

296
00:14:15,570 --> 00:14:17,640
