297
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:20,070
He's learning Go from a famous master.

298
00:14:20,290 --> 00:14:21,940
He's been busy and couldn't be here.

299
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,670
Let me take you all inside to look.

300
00:14:25,090 --> 00:14:26,190
- Sure!
- Let's go.

301
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:44,560
My lord.

302
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:45,880
The leader has left.

303
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:46,910
Will Lu Wen still come?

304
00:14:47,450 --> 00:14:48,580
Knowing Lu Wen,

305
00:14:49,170 --> 00:14:50,170
he won't let this

306
00:14:50,170 --> 00:14:51,670
end so easily.

307
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,810
Besides, Liu Miantang

308
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:55,100
reacted to that code.

309
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,220
Let's wait and see.

310
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,150
It's so beautiful.

311
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,670
Indeed, it's quite nice.

312
00:15:19,210 --> 00:15:21,270
I heard the garrison's nephew has gone missing.

313
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,580
That guy is probably

314
00:15:23,090 --> 00:15:24,410
off somewhere causing trouble.

315
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:25,430
It's true.

316
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:27,340
His family's been searching for days.

317
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,460
I bet

318
00:15:30,090 --> 00:15:31,510
he offended someone.

319
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:35,170
My lord.

320
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,310
Chen Tu is missing.

321
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,620
Didn't you say to leave him alone?

322
00:15:44,690 --> 00:15:45,620
So what?

323
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,100
What does it have to do with me?

324
00:15:56,330 --> 00:15:57,170
Young man.

325
00:16:00,810 --> 00:16:01,810
You've eaten three buns

326
00:16:01,810 --> 00:16:03,120
at my door.

327
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,220
Do you want to come inside?

328
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,690
- I...
- We've just opened.

329
00:16:06,690 --> 00:16:07,530
Come in and look.

330
00:16:11,170 --> 00:16:12,010
Please.

331
00:16:15,970 --> 00:16:16,810
My lord.

332
00:16:17,090 --> 00:16:18,580
She invited our shadow guard inside.

333
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,080
This...

334
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:27,190
Do you like this design?

335
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,640
This is a special design

336
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:31,340
